<p style="font-size:22px">Police later arrested Vikas Fhatak and his aide Ikrar Khan for orchestrating the protest in Dharavi where over a 1,000 students, mostly minors, blocked the roads and some of them took to violence, damaging vehicles, including police vehicles, and were lathi-charged by police. He was produced before a magistrate court in Bandra and remanded in police custody, along with his aide till February 4.</p>



